invalid type: string "Monopoly. The Monopoly cards are similar to Empire cards and the game is fast,\n\njust like Monopoly Empire.\n\n\n[Check Price](https://geni.us/ZuQAWRE)\n\n### 4. The Logo Board Game\n\n\nWhile this one’s not a Monopoly game, it features many of the brands that you’ll\n\nsee in Monopoly Empire. Two to four players move around the board answering\n\nquestions as they go.\n